      <li>
        <a href="http://www.polygon.com/features/2016/2/2/10885790/valve-htc-vive-preview-games" class="m-carousel__img vox-lazy-load" data-analytics-link="feature:image" data-original="https://cdn1.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/EcSthXBCaniBDd33rVneDaKowXA=/701x0:3245x3816/347x520/cdn0.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/48697745/Vive_CloseUp.0.0.jpg" data-ratio="0.6666666666666666" data-imgkey="48697745:portrait:8"></a>

        <div class="meta">
            <a class="type" href="http://www.polygon.com/features">Feature</a>
          <a class="title" data-analytics-link="feature" href="http://www.polygon.com/features/2016/2/2/10885790/valve-htc-vive-preview-games">This is how Vive beats the Rift: Games and packed-in motion controls</a>
          <a class="byline" href="http://www.polygon.com/features/2016/2/2/10885790/valve-htc-vive-preview-games">Ben Kuchera</a>
        </div>
